{"tid":433912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】幫手捉賊","createTime":"2017-10-12T20:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T00:04:50.000Z","uid":146007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10d5750ae64b44d770bafa22c633b6c883f9deaa","tid":433912,"uid":146007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T20:07:31.000Z","msg":"件事係咁嘅，<br />\n小妹學校間宿舍有人偷內衣褲<br />\n偷晾係天台嘅內衣褲<br />\n我仲要俾佢偷左個最近新買嘅bra，小小貴（對我黎講）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左自己都仲有其他女仔俾人偷<br />\n<br />\n上年係洗衣房已經被人偷左個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係晾係天台個啲就冇人偷過<br />\n所以今年洗完啲衫同內衣褲繼續晾係天台，點知就。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>所以小妹想問有冇巴絲打可以借/平租幾個細嘅攝影機俾我放係天台影住。因為諗住放廿四小時去影，所以最好就算夜晚個機都有番咁上下功能去影到係邊個</strong><br />\n<br />\n報警應該都冇咩用，如果要學校裝Cam應該都要十世，但係我唔想俾個賊人再放肆落去！！！所以希望各位巴絲打可以幫幫手"},{"pid":"05cd665d0050448501258ad00b6db5c0daca5f58","tid":433912,"uid":90787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T20:19:45.000Z","msg":"bra圖呢"},{"pid":"1b9f779f7d9e7024fda1d66529b1e9acbd25c040","tid":433912,"uid":28660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T21:11:57.000Z","msg":"晾返係自己間房咪唔驚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b12859e8b4911fc13f6fa8bebc5d0fb6527ad0","tid":433912,"uid":146007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T23:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bra圖呢</blockquote><br />\n俾人偷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb02378672872e36030b2d616004bfc4b2191e73","tid":433912,"uid":146007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晾返係自己間房咪唔驚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之後會，但係我想捉個賊"},{"pid":"5c90e7c1591a28146e4e18503d7cb59ccbb59bbd","tid":433912,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>bra圖呢</blockquote><br />\n俾人偷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n示意圖都好<br />\n乜都無搵對奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}